<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/jan/18/">&#x27a0;</a> January 18, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="what_works_in_software_develop" >

        
        <a name="002226"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://mungus.schwern.org/~schwern/talks/What_Works_In_Software_Development/What_Works/">What Works In Software Development</a></h4>

        

        <p>A really good summary of the best bits of Agile, XP, etc. plus some common sense.  Turns a bit Perl-centric near the end, but that aside it&#8217;s an excellent read for software engineers.</p>

