<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/oct/05/">&#x27a0;</a> October 5, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="a_lot_of_people_have_the_phone" >

        
        <a name="002051"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.google.com/search?hl=en&amp;lr=&amp;c2coff=1&amp;q=214-748-3647&amp;btnG=Search">A lot of people have the phone number (214) 748-3647</a></h4>

        

        <p>Which, coincidentally, is the largest number that can be held in a 32-bit integer.  Remember, kids:  Just because it&#8217;s a number, doesn&#8217;t mean you should store it in a number database field.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
